    <item>
      <title>林赛·格雷厄姆的去世改变了他的民主党挑战者的竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/13/us/politics/annie-andrews-south-carolina-senate.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[儿科医生安妮·安德鲁斯在考虑格雷厄姆去世造成的政治影响的同时，向那些热爱格雷厄姆的人们表示哀悼。共和党人正忙于安排新的初选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/13/us/politics/annie-andrews-south-carolina-senate.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 22:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
